<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5341136>
    dc:description "Figs 1-10: (1) Eremnophila and (2) Ammophila: lateral view of anterior half of thorax (es = episternal sulcus); (3) Podalonia: gastral segments I-II lateral and ventral; (4) Ammophila: gastral segments I-II lateral and ventral; (5) Parapsammophila and (6) Eremochares: posterior view of petiole socket, hindcoxa, and propodeal sternite (solid black); (7) lateral view of hindtarsal claw with basal tooth; (8) Hoplammophila: male genitalia; (9) Parapsammophila: foretarsomere I of female; (10) Hoplammophila: foretarsomere I of female; (BOHART & MENKE 1976)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5341136/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

